title: WTF | Watch: Pack of wild Russian dogs trolled by laser pointer
text:
All we'll say is that whoever is behind the pointer is lucky they're at the top of an apartment block and the dogs have no way to find them because if they did we doubt the end result would be pretty.
Endless hours of entertainment, none the less.
Via YouTube
